      <title>二级域名及vercel绑定</title>
      <link href="/2025/06/19/2025.6.19/"/>
      <url>/2025/06/19/2025.6.19/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h3><p>这里默认大家已经拥有自己的域名，创建二级域名主要目的是：<br>在你主域名已经绑定的前提下，不想重新再买一个域名进行别的网站的绑定</p><h3 id="创建二级域名"><a href="#创建二级域名" class="headerlink" title="创建二级域名"></a>创建二级域名</h3><p>打开你购买域名的官网（这里以<a href="https://www.aliyun.com/">阿里云</a>为例）</p><blockquote><p>[!TIP]</p><p>搜索域名控制台，进入域名管理</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620173247119.png" alt="image-20250620173247119"></p><blockquote><p>[!TIP]</p><p>进入<strong>域名列表</strong>，点击解析</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620173415215.png" alt="image-20250620173415215"></p><blockquote><p>[!TIP]</p><p>点击<strong>添加域名</strong>，填入域名的名字<strong>前缀不能是大写</strong></p></blockquote><h6 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620173742135.png" alt="image-20250620173742135"></h6><blockquote><p>[!TIP]</p><p>点击<strong>TXT授权校验</strong>，保存TXT记录</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620173948316.png" alt="image-20250620173948316"></p><blockquote><p>[!TIP]</p><p>进入主域名的<strong>解析设置</strong>，<strong>这里一定得是主域名！</strong></p></blockquote><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620174108097.png" alt="image-20250620174108097"></p><blockquote><p>[!TIP]</p><p><strong>添加记录</strong>，将记录填入，<strong>记录类型要选择TXT</strong></p></blockquote><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620174343636.png" alt="image-20250620174343636"></p><blockquote><p>[!TIP]</p><p>返回进行TXT检测</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620174610973.png" alt="image-20250620174610973"></p><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620174649423.png" alt="image-20250620174649423"></p><h3 id="将域名解析至vercel"><a href="#将域名解析至vercel" class="headerlink" title="将域名解析至vercel"></a>将域名解析至vercel</h3><blockquote><p>[!NOTE]</p><p>这里假设你已经在vercel上面创建好项目，准备绑定域名</p></blockquote><ul><li><p>进入项目，点击<strong>Domains</strong></p><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620181547727.png" alt="image-20250620181547727"></p></li><li><p>点击<strong>add domains</strong>，输入你的域名并保存</p><blockquote><p>[!IMPORTANT]</p><p>你会看到Invalid Configuration的警告，这是因为你还没有配置</p></blockquote></li><li><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620181638318.png" alt="image-20250620181638318"></p></li><li><p>点击进入解析页面，将记录值保存下来</p><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620181713838.png" alt="image-20250620181713838"></p></li><li><p>回到阿里云域名列表，对你的二级域名解析设置</p><blockquote><p>[!IMPORTANT]</p><p>是刚刚创建的二级域名!        </p></blockquote></li><li><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620181759564.png" alt=""></p></li><li><p>添加两条解析记录</p><blockquote><p>[!IMPORTANT]</p><p>第一条基本是一样的，记录值不是76.76.21.21</p><p>第二条就要看你的记录填了</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://m1kasaz-typora.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/image-20250620181823482.png" alt="image-20250620181823482"></p></li><li><p>返回vercel，正常情况下你的域名就绑定成功了</p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
